getStartTime = (lapNumber) => {
    row = from(bucket: "${bucketName2}")
        |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
        |> filter(fn: (r) => r["lap_time"] == "lap_number")
        |> filter(fn: (r) => r._value == int(v: lapNumber))
        |> group()
        |> first()
        |> findRecord(fn: (key) => true, idx:0)
    return row._time
}

getFinishTime = (lapNumber) => {
    row = from(bucket: "${bucketName2}")
        |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
        |> filter(fn: (r) => r["lap_time"] == "lap_number")
        |> filter(fn: (r) => r._value == int(v: lapNumber))
        |> group()
        |> last()
        |> findRecord(fn: (key) => true, idx:0)
    return row._time
}

from(bucket: "${bucketName2}")
  |> range(start: getStartTime(lapNumber: ${lap1}), stop: getFinishTime(lapNumber: ${lap1}))
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "gps")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "latitude" or r["_field"] == "longitude")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["ID"] == "gps_position")
  |> aggregateWindow(every: v.windowPeriod, fn: mean)

start_time = getStartTime(lapNumber: ${lap1})
start_time2 = getStartTime(lapNumber: ${lap2})

hour1 = date.hour(t: start_time)
minute1 = date.minute(t: start_time)

hours = hour2 - hour1

secondos = total_sec * 1000000000
test2 = duration(v: uint(v: secondos))
